fields.name: Tesla Cybertruck Tri Motor 2023
fields.description: Since Tesla manufactures the Cybertruck, there obviously has to be an obnoxious performance variant. The top trim Cybertruck utilizes a tri-motor setup and can accelerate from zero to sixty in under three seconds, which is impressive for any vehicle, let alone a trapezoidal prism with four wheels.
fields.list: Range: 500+ miles / Drivetrain: AWD / Acceleration: 0-60 in <2.9 seconds / Towing Capacity: 14.000+ pounds
